<h1>Projects</h1>
<p>Projects will be one of the most important activities of the Center.</p>
<p>Experts from the Center and Industry will come out with challenging problem statements which will be assigned to the students of RVCE. </p>
<p>Each project will have a team of students, one Faculty guide and a project mentor. </p>
<p>As on now,about 6 projects have been assigned to different teams and they have already started the literature survey. </p>
<p>There will be frequent interaction sessions with students, project guide and the mentor to assess the progress of the project work. </p>
<p>Projects are related to developing AI and ML based algorithms to analyse and extract content in an intelligent manner from live video surveillance camera feeds.</p>